Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:02.95,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Success! Integrity! Evidence and its impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.95,0:00:04.79,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}An endless drive to become the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.79,0:00:06.30,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Even twisted love can’t get through this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:09.40,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A locked room murder in a car sealed from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.90,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.68,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:14.30,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
