Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.46,0:01:32.13,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Masato Sato
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:02:00.53,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}After the battle with the Black Organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:03.25,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}we returned to a tranquil existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:09.25,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That’s when Eisuke Hondo, a student who looked just like Kir,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:11.18,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}transferred to Ran’s High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:16.36,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Well, Eisuke turned out to be a clumsy boy who is a big fan of the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:21.41,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But then a client came by, asking us to find his girlfriend who had driven off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:28.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Did you two really meet on this freezing mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:31.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind those trees! That’s my car!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:33.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami! Ami!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:37.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The doors are lined with duct tape from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:42.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And there’s a charcoal stove on the front passenger seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:49.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a case of carbon monoxide poisoning by burning charcoal inside an enclosed space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:53.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s clearly suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:54.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:57.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is a murder, skillfully set up to look like a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:58.88,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And the culprit is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:01.32,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A suicide, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we’d better wrap up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:18.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll need you to come to the station for questioning later on, but that’s all for today—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:19.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just tripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:33.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there’s a depression in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:40.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the shape,\Nsomebody parked their car here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:43.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could have parked here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:48.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s about the same size as the car we rode up in with the beardy man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:53.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, when did you rent that car?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:55.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:04:02.28,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsushi Misumi (32)\NClient
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:04:02.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After the fight, Ami said she wanted to use the car the next day,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I needed a car too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:07.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I went out and rented one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:11.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought she’d use my car for something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:14.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re such a silly man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:21.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you knew she was going to take your car, why’d you leave your work in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:26.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was going to get it in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:30.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:34.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The project proposal he needs to present to his company tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:39.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He hired me to find his girlfriend because he needed those papers back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, did you get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:44.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, no, I haven’t looked yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:46.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that you mention it, the documents should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:52.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, did you find some documents in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:56.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We found some paperwork in the back seat of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:59.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that’d be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:02.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find them? That’s great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:07.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We also found a purse that seems to have belonged to the deceased...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and found this inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:13.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a cigarette lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:19.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what was it doing in her purse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:20.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:26.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was also a brand-new book, just published today, with a fresh burn mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:29.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it looks like the lighter was placed in the purse recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:34.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason we didn’t find any fingerprints on the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:38.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This gets weirder by the minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:41.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She hated cigarettes, but I’m a heavy smoker,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:45.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so sometimes she’d hide the cigarette lighter from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:47.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she put it in her bag out of habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:50.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a heavy smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:55.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if I go smoke a cigarette in the rental car?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:58.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I held myself back today and barely smoked at all, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:05:59.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cigarette...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:06.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:13.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:27.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The killer has to be that Misumi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Out you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:32.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The only question is how he did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:37.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:39.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Eisuke-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:44.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I’m always the one who slips and falls into the slush.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:47.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you’re bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:51.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I must’ve cut my finger on the broken windshield.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:55.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I have a bandage on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:56.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stick your finger out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:06:59.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:14.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just a little scratch! He’s fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:18.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least let me bandage it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:21.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:28.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}These bandages are so amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:34.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it seals my finger perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:38.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s like the cut never existed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:44.52,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait a minute. That duct tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:46.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Excuse me, Mr. Forensic Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:53.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I left something in the car when I went in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:04.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So that’s how he did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:10.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It was suicide! Su-i-cide!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:15.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-{\i1}san{\i0} was inside this car,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:18.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the doors were sealed with duct tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:23.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We found a charcoal stove with burnt charcoal beside her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:28.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So forget about capturing Sleeping Kogoro on tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:39.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with you two? You should be glad this isn’t a murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:44.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But everybody at the station was hoping to see my video of Sleeping Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For the love of...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:54.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed something funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:55.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:58.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What’s gotten into you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:02.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the car door!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:04.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:05.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:09.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from the duct tape and the shattered window, it looks normal enough to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:17.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:24.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir? What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:29.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That proud pose and scornful attitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:31.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s Sleeping Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not scornful! I’m confident!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But sir, if you’re sitting down like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:39.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Does it mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:44.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right! It’s time for Sleeping Kogoro to make a deduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:46.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:51.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The most important figure in this case should be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:55.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...the victim’s boyfriend, Misumi-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:19.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Mouri’s deduction show?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:24.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami committed suicide, didn’t she?\NWhat is there to deduce?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:28.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there’s plenty to unravel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:32.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this was a murder made to look like a suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:34.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:37.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And the killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:41.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the person who entered the car under the pretence of rescuing Ami-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:44.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then proceeded to cut the duct tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:47.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you, Atsushi Misumi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:53.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Really? I never guessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:58.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? That’s Sleeping Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:00.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s just talking with his head down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:03.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s not asleep or possessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:07.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:09.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But doesn’t it strike you as odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:11.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:15.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy standing next to Mouri-{\i1}san{\i0}, behind the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:18.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:21.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He often helps out with Dad’s deductions!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s standing by in case Dad needs something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:29.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve got to be joking, Mouri-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:33.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m the one who hired you to find her, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:39.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You set us up from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:43.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You needed to trick us into believing this car was completely sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:46.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Trick you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:47.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don’t mean to be rude, Mouri-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:51.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but the car {\i1}was{\i0} sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:56.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The forensics team said they had a tough time pulling the duct tape off the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:58.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:01.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was the door on the {\i1}driver’s{\i0} side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:04.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What if the duct tape on the {\i1}passenger{\i0} side...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:08.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...had slits cut in it from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:08.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:12.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you saw it yourself, didn’t you, Mouri-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:16.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw him cut through the duct tape with a utility knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:18.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I was watching him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:23.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He put his hand over a piece of duct tape that had been stuck lightly over the slits,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:27.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and cut neatly through them as he pushed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:32.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the car wasn’t sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:35.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First Misumi-{\i1}san{\i0} brings his girlfriend here in his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:40.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He drugs her on the way over by spiking her coffee with sleeping pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:44.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he moves her into the driver’s seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:48.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and seals the edges of all the doors with duct tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:56.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, he cuts through the duct tape on the passenger side, so he can exit the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:13:03.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He hangs some strips of tape lightly over the slits to conceal them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:09.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he lights the charcoal,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:12.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,gets out of the car, and shuts the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All he needs to do after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:19.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is drive home in a rental car he’d parked at the scene earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then get someone to come with him to “find” the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:27.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He has his patsy check the door on the driver’s side,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:30.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then quickly smashes through the windshield to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:35.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He makes a show of cutting through the tape on the passenger side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:39.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Voilà{\i0}, a locked-room murder inside a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:44.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When we saw her slumped in the driver’s seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:47.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of course we tried to get in through the driver’s side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:53.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We assumed the passenger side was sealed just as tightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:57.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pressing down on the decoy strips of tape stuck them to the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:14:02.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so even if we checked later, we probably wouldn’t notice the gimmick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:09.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how the tape has been cut on the passenger side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:11.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:16.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The cuts on the horizontal and vertical strips of tape are slightly off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:21.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s because Misumi cut through the horizontal strips first,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:23.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the vertical strips later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:31.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the driver’s seat was pulled back and her jacket was creased because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:36.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. Misumi-{\i1}san{\i0} drove the car here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:40.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and moved his girlfriend into the driver’s seat after she passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:42.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:47.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was desperately trying to save my girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:52.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe you’d suspect me of {\i1}killing{\i0} her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not like there’s any proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:56.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:01.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the car’s ash tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:07.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that cigarette lighter in her bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:13.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She put it there not only to stop Misumi-{\i1}san{\i0} from smoking inside the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:17.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but also to prevent him from finding something before she left the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:21.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing she’d hidden in the ash tray:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:23.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A farewell letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:26.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:28.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,“I guess you want to take me to the place where we met,”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:32.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,“so we can go back to the way we were in the past,”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:36.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,“but it won’t work. I’ve changed. I’m sorry.”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:37.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s signed, “Ami”.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:41.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She{\i0} was the one who’d changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:45.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}you{\i0} were the one who wanted to come out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:49.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If this letter was written by the victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:50.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it proves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:51.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It’s a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami was trying to frame me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:56.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She committed suicide and made it look like I killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:00.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She could’ve cut the duct tape beforehand, putting the utility knife
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:04.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,into the glove compartment so I’d be likely to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:07.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And she wrote that letter to pin the crime on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:10.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The letter isn’t the proof I was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:14.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is the book cover it was written on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll know when you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:20.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s one of those paper covers that bookstores use to wrap books for customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:25.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably came off the brand-new book we found in your girlfriend’s purse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:32.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn’t find any fingerprints on the book because you wiped them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:38.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You bought it as a gift for her, so your prints were all over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:44.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you forgot about the book cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:51.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She wrote that letter on it and hid it in the ash tray for you to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:59.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you’d like to explain how your fingerprints got on a cover that was just purchased today,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:05.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and was found inside a car you supposedly haven’t been in since sometime yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:11.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can’t tell if the cover came from that book...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:16.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Books are all different sizes, even if they belong to the same series.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:20.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A cover that fits the book so perfectly is rather uncommon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:24.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should we take a trip to the bookstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:28.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet we’ll find a clerk who remembers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:30.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That the man who bought the book this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:35.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,had bloodshot eyes, haunted by the crime he was planning to commit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:44.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bloodshot eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:47.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re wrong there, Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:52.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably looked hopeless and defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:56.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,knowing it was the last favor I’d do for the woman I loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:18:00.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked you to buy the book?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:06.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right. You’ll find my prints all over the cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:10.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I did everything she wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:16.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I fulfilled that woman’s every desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:18.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she said she wanted to go somewhere on vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:20.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’d take time off work and make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she said she wanted to see some popular singer in concert,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:25.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’d stand in line all night to get tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:28.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:32.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I went into debt to buy the model she wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:38.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right... I felt like her Prince Charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:42.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I finally realized I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:45.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was no prince to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:47.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...just a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:50.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:52.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a cigarette in her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:55.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A brand I don’t smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:58.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I quit smoking for her too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:01.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was cheating on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:09.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I confronted her, she admitted she’d gone out with another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:12.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She even laughed about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:15.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:18.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Paying off the loan on that car,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:20.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so some other guy could drive around town with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:24.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that’s why you killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:26.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:28.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:31.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved her from the bottom of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:34.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t come here just to complete the crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:37.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was partly for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:39.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was filled with guilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:42.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hoped maybe she was still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:45.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I smashed through the windshield...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:55.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know what went on between you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:59.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know your so-called love for her was long over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:04.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really wanted to save her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:10.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you would have carefully broken the rear window or the window on the passenger side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:16.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By smashing wildly at the windshield,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:21.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you sprayed her with broken glass and could have severely injured her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:26.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You already knew she was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:32.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just wanted to destroy your past with her, along with the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:08.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You were amazing, Sleeping Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:11.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your deduction echoed through the snow-capped mountains of Gunma!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:14.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m gonna show this video to everybody at the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:16.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:20.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I don’t remember a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:22.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}On her lap again ...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:25.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Huh? I only got one shot of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:31.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I kept pausing it so I wouldn’t waste the tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:34.86,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He forgot to take it off pause.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.86,0:22:38.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Can we go back and redo it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:40.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nuts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:45.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really helped crack the case today, Eisuke-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:46.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:49.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0} noticed there was something suspicious about the duct tape in the car
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:52.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because of what you said about the bandage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:22:55.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he ran and told my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:58.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:01.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Another sleuth beat you to it today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:03.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:06.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s his usual thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:09.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He always makes some funny comment that has nothing to do with the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:12.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it gets people on track to the real solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:13.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}D-Don’t tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:17.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This kid does?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.15,0:23:20.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}D-Don’t tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:24.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Is this guy on to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:32.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If you’re such a fan of Sleeping Kogoro, feel free to drop by anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:34.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:36.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:38.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.55,0:23:44.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Nah, couldn’t be.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:46.93,0:23:50.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0004,,{\be10}And perhaps if he couldn’t achieve his objective...
Dialogue: 1,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.63,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0004,,{\be10}...the culprit’s next action would be...
Dialogue: 1,0:23:54.23,0:23:55.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0004,,{\be10}...a kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.76,0:24:01.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Next Conan:
